descriptionHtml:
Body Temp tracker and smart thermometer App Data is an application to store and share the body temperature records measured by the medical thermometer. You'll be able indeed the track temperature ranges of your body on chart based on information saved using this infrared thermometer tracker.

Fever stimulates your body to mobilize and produce more white blood cells and antibodies to fight infections.

Body Temperature Fever tracker app is used to generate graphs statistical analysis and reports on the basis of entered reports. Digital Thermometer app has info and guidelines section which helps the user to get updated accordingly. This Body Temperature Diary History: Fever Check Thermometer tracker App gives you all functions you need to track, record and analyze your body temperature and pulse.

Whether you have been exposed to low temperatures or you are caring for someone with hypothermia, you may need to know how to increase body temperature.

Dynamic graphs measure.
Choose reminder times to suit you.
Track over a day, week, month and more.
Track your temperature using this free app.
Maintain records and have summarized values.
Follow the info and guidelines to get better health.
Provide complete user info in order to enable the application to calculate your BMI.
